{"title":"斥黎某反华","authors":["黄文欢"],"dates":[{"year":1979,"month":11,"day":28}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"斥黎某反华"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄文欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得意忘形气焰高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反华语恶口滔滔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"引狼入室前功废，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以友为仇后果糟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚂蚁夸槐空自大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蚍蜉撼树只徒劳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无情历史将宣判，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祸国殃民罪不饶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九七九年十一月二十三日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（这是黄文欢同志在北京用中文写的诗。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（新华社北京二十七日电）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":5,"page_end":5}